Judul: ART Tennis balls  and trash  enliven a  lesser-known  dimension of  Pablo Picasso
Abstrak: The article reviews the "Picasso Sculpture" art exhibition which runs through February 7, 2016 at the Museum of Modern Art in New York, New York and features several sculptures by the late Spanish artist Pablo Picasso including "Guitar," and it mentions the use of tennis balls and trash in art.
Sumber: Time. 9/28/2015, Vol. 186 Issue 12, p59-60. 2p. 5 Color Photographs.
